{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ODDCORE</strong> is a first person, retro-inspired boomer shooter with roguelike ingredients that is packed with endless, brain-rotting visuals of your bullets exploding everything that they touch. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>FULL FEATURES:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">we're cooking. TBA</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>FOR NOW, IF THE ODDCORE IS CALLING YOUR NAME\u00a0</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong> please read the letter below, thank you\u00a0</strong>\u2193</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>To YOU, YES YOU</strong>,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Congratulation on landing this gig with us! Here is the run down of the job:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are now an ODDCORE runner AND you have been employed to protect the core of our memories one variant at a time. No 2 sessions are the same.\u00a0<strong>Deploy each run with new loadouts, manage time wisely and eradicate the corrupted hordes from taking over the ODDCORE.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2896260/extras/equip.gif?t=1737780007\" /><u><strong>EQUIP YOURSELF FOR DEPLOYMENT</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Jump into the ODDCORE with your own load-out, combining a variety of weapons and gadgets. Prove yourself to be the best among us.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2896260/extras/GIF4_1_1.gif?t=1737780007\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>ERADICATE CORRUPTED ENTITIES</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Preserving our memories one kill at a time. A bullet a day keeps the ODD away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i